OL,3,CIndian-Nepalese restaurant targeted in
OL,4,C'racially-motivated' arson attack
OL,6,FA fire at an Indian-Nepalese
OL,7,Frestaurant in Newtownabbey is being
OL,8,Ftreated as a hate crime after racist
OL,9,Fgraffiti was sprayed on a wall and the
OL,10,Fpremises was set alight overnight.
OL,12,FPolice received a report of arson
OL,13,Fwhich is thought to have occurred at
OL,14,Fthe licensed premises in the
OL,15,FBallyclare Road area on Wednesday, 21
OL,16,FAugust.
