OL,3,CIndian-Nepalese restaurant targeted in
OL,4,C'racially-motivated' arson attack
OL,6,FIn the early hours of Wednesday
OL,7,Fmorning, parts of the Ballyclare Road
OL,8,Fwere closed as firefighters dealt with
OL,9,Fthe blaze at The Railway Bar and Steam
OL,10,FDining restaurant.
OL,12,FIn a statement issued on Wednesday,
OL,13,Fthe PSNI confirmed that the incident
OL,14,Fwas deliberate and is being treated as
OL,15,Fa racially-motivated hate crime.
OL,17,FSinn Fein MP John Finucane described
OL,18,Fthe attack as 'sickening and
OL,19,Fdeplorable'.
