OL,3,CIndian-Nepalese restaurant targeted in
OL,4,C'racially-motivated' arson attack
OL,6,FThe North Belfast MP said: "The racist
OL,7,Fattack on a business in Newtownabbey
OL,8,Fin the early hours of this morning was
OL,9,Fabsolutely sickening and deplorable.
OL,11,F"This business operates to serve our
OL,12,Fcommunity and employ workers. It is
OL,13,Ftotally unacceptable that it has been
OL,14,Ftargeted in this way.
OL,16,F"These disgusting and disgraceful
OL,17,Fattacks which are fuelled by racism,
OL,18,Fhatred and discrimination have no
OL,19,Fplace in our inclusive and forward-
OL,20,Flooking society.
