OL,6,F"Those intent on causing hate and
OL,7,Fstirring up division must face the
OL,8,Ffull force of the law, and I would
OL,9,Fappeal to anyone who may have
OL,10,Finformation on this incident to bring
OL,11,Fit forward to police."
OL,13,FDetective Sergeant Crothers added: "At
OL,14,Faround 1.50am, it was reported that a
OL,15,Fproperty was set alight in the area.
OL,16,FGraffiti was also reported on the
OL,17,Fpremises following the incident.
